<h1>Step 3 ŌĆö Update your registry <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">primary_file</code> so nothing points to quarantined files</h1>
