</ul>
<p>Good news: this specific paper is <strong>Open Access on SpringerLink</strong> and the page explicitly says ŌĆ£You have full accessŌĆØ and provides <strong>Download PDF</strong>. <span class="inline-flex p-0.5" data-state="closed"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s13201-021-01456-8" class="focus-visible:ring-ring inline-flex rounded-sm no-underline focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2"><span class="bg-surface-raised inline-flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-sm p-0.5 cursor-pointer"><span class="text-center font-['Inter'] text-[10px] font-normal leading-3 text-interactive-link">1</span></span></a></span></p>
