<h1>Step 8 (the real next milestone): TEI ŌåÆ section-aware chunks (Methods/Validation/Preprocessing)</h1>
<p>Now that you have <strong>253 included TEIs</strong>, we should move to chunking.</p>
<h3>What ŌĆ£chunkingŌĆØ must do for your review RQs</h3>
<p>For each TEI, output chunks with:</p>
<ul>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">paper_id</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">tei_path</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">section</code> (best effort from TEI structure)</li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">text</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">char_count</code></li>
<li>(optional) <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">is_methods_like</code> boolean based on section headings</li>
</ul>
