tive-normal h-5 w-5 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="M6 9L12 15L18 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></button><div class="relative z-0 w-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 ease-out" style="height:0px;opacity:0"><div><div class="relative z-0 flex flex-col px-3 pb-3"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://gist.github.com/Achionye/ca782340e7ab67d7a152c94c00717185" class="text-interactive-link hover:bg-surface-secondary focus-visible:ring-ring group flex min-h-[80px] w-full items-center justify-start gap-2 self-stretch overflow-hidden rounded-xl p-2 no-underline focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-inset sm:min-h-[96px] sm:gap-4 [&amp;::after]:content-none" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col items-start justify-center gap-2 overflow-hidden"><div class="flex w-full min-w-0 items-center justify-start gap-2"><div class="border-border-faint/30 relative h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-lg border"><img alt="favicon" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy" width="32" height="32" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="object-cover" style="color:transparent" src="https://github.githubassets.com/favicons/favicon.svg"></div><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col items-start justify-start gap-0.5"><div class="flex w-full min-w-0 items-start justify-start gap-1"><div class="bg-surface-raised mt-0.5 inline-flex w-4 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded p-0.5"><p class="text-interactive-link text-center text-[10px] leading-3">1</p></div><p class="text-text-primary min-w-0 flex-1 truncate text-sm font-medium leading-tight">Oguta review: CORE scripts (text-only)</p></div><p class="text-interactive-link w-full truncate text-xs leading-normal">https://gist.github.com/Achionye/ca782340e7ab67d7a152c94c00717185</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-surface-secondary relative hidden aspect-video w-1/4 max-w-[220px] overflow-hidden rounded-lg min-[425px]:block"><img alt="preview" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-cover" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="https://arena.ai/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.githubassets.com%2Fassets%2Fgist-og-image-54fd7dc0713e.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=85"></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="prose prose-sm prose-pre:bg-transparent prose-pre:p-0 text-wrap break-words"><p>Your <strong>ŌĆ£Included missing TEI: 55ŌĆØ is now mostly a <em>linking/DOI-parsing issue</em>, not a lack of TEI files.</strong> You proved you have TEIs (366 OK), but <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">tei_coverage_vs_included_v2.py</code> is currently extracting DOIs in a way that can accidentally swallow the file extension (because it runs the DOI regex on <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">p.name</code>, and your DOI regex allows dots; then <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">norm_doi()</code> does not strip suffixes/punctuation). ThatŌĆÖs exactly how a filename like <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">10.1371_journal.pntd.0009634.tei.xml</code> can yield a ŌĆ£DOIŌĆØ that looks like <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">10.1371/journal.pntd.0009634.tei.xml</code> and therefore wonŌĆÖt match your registry DOI. <span class="inline-flex p-0.5" data-state="closed"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://gist.github.com/Achionye/ca782340e7ab67d7a152c94c00717185" class="focus-visible:ring-ring inline-flex rounded-sm no-underline focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2"><span class="bg-surface-raised inline-flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-sm p-0.5 cursor-pointer"><span class="text-center font-['Inter'] text-[10px] font-normal leading-3 text-interactive-link">1</span></span></a></span></p>
<h2>Step 1 ŌĆö Patch <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">tei_coverage_vs_included_v2.py</code> (two tiny edits, high yield)</h2>
<p>Open: <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">.\scripts\tei_coverage_vs_included_v2.py</code> and change <strong>only</strong> these functions.</p>
