<p>If <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">docker ps</code> still gives the same <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">dockerDesktopLinuxEngine</code> pipe error, Docker Desktop is not running (or not installed / WSL2 backend not enabled).</p>
