<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">tei_coverage_vs_included_v2.py</code> only counts a TEI as ŌĆ£coveringŌĆØ an included study if it can extract a <strong>DOI</strong> from either <strong>(a)</strong> the TEI filename (it tries <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">name.replace("_","/")</code> and then DOI-regex) or <strong>(b)</strong> inside the TEI text (<code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">&lt;idno type="doi"&gt;ŌĆ”&lt;/idno&gt;</code> or any DOI regex match). <span class="inline-flex p-0.5" data-state="closed"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://gist.github.com/Achionye/ca782340e7ab67d7a152c94c00717185" class="focus-visible:ring-ring inline-flex rounded-sm no-underline focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2"><span class="bg-surface-raised inline-flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-sm p-0.5 cursor-pointer"><span class="text-center font-['Inter'] text-[10px] font-normal leading-3 text-interactive-link">1</span></span></a></span></li>
<li>Right now, across your whole project, you only have <strong>76 TEIs with extractable DOIs</strong>, and only <strong>5</strong> of those DOIs are in your <strong>268 included</strong> DOIs. So the ŌĆ£missing TEIŌĆØ count is huge mainly because <strong>you do not yet have TEI fulltexts generated (or DOI-identifiable) for your included PDF corpus</strong>ŌĆöthe TEIs you found are mostly from other folders (e.g., <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">openalex_expansion\tei_trimmed\...</code>) and/or TEIs where DOI isnŌĆÖt present/recognized. <span class="inline-flex p-0.5" data-state="closed"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://gist.github.com/Achionye/ca782340e7ab67d7a152c94c00717185" class="focus-visible:ring-ring inline-flex rounded-sm no-underline focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2"><span class="bg-surface-raised inline-flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-sm p-0.5 cursor-pointer"><span class="text-center font-['Inter'] text-[10px] font-normal leading-3 text-interactive-link">1</span></span></a></span></li>
