<h2>2) <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">gh gist create</code> (CLI) does <strong>not</strong> upload binary files like <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">.zip</code></h2>
<p>ThatŌĆÖs why you got:</p>
