<span class="line"><span>Get-ChildItem -Recurse -File |</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>  Where-Object { $_.Extension -match '\.(py|ps1|json|yml|yaml|toml|env|txt|md)$' } |</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>  ForEach-Object {</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>    $hits = Select-String -Path $_.FullName -Pattern "api[_-]?key|token|secret|bearer|OPENAI|SERPAPI|password" -SimpleMatch -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>    if ($hits) { $_.FullName }</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>  } |</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>  Sort-Object -Unique</span></span></code></pre></div></div></pre>
<p>If you find secrets:</p>
<ul>
<li>replace with placeholders like <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">YOUR_API_KEY_HERE</code></li>
<li>or move secrets into a non-shared file like <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">.env</code> (and donŌĆÖt gist it)</li>
</ul>
