<h1>Step 5 ŌĆö Paste the Gist link here</h1>
<p>Once you paste it, IŌĆÖll do this immediately (in order, no reinvention):</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Read your current pipeline</strong> and infer the ŌĆ£true run graphŌĆØ (what depends on what).</li>
