<p>And IŌĆÖll keep everything PowerShell-friendly (entrypoints you can run like <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">.\run_step3_chunk.ps1</code> etc.).</p>
<hr>
<h2>One non-negotiable to make this ŌĆ£not limitedŌĆØ</h2>
<p>Along with your scripts, please include <strong>any one</strong> of these if you have it:</p>
<ul>
<li><code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">requirements.txt</code> or <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">environment.yml</code> or <code class="rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-surface-tertiary font-mono text-[0.9em] text-text-primary font-medium" node="[object Object]">pyproject.toml</code></li>
